title: Soundtrack - The Saint [1997]
description:
The Saint: Music From The Motion Picture Soundtrack was the soundtrack to the 1997 movie The Saint.
This soundtrack featuring Duran Duran, Sneaker Pimps, Orbital, Moby, Fluke, Luscious Jackson, The Chemical Brothers, Underworld, Daft Punk, David Bowie, Superior, Dreadzone, Duncan Sheik, and Everything but the Girl. The album also includes an updated version of the theme music from the 1960s television series.
